      "content": "so if the iron is still physically there in the soil but just \"unavailable\" because it's bonded to other stuff, it sounds like the nutrients are being hidden or stolen from the plant even though they're right there. is there any way to tell if it's just a pH issue or if there's something else actually interfering with the uptake?",
